Tool

NameImport TMS Image
ID9
AuthorO.Conrad (c) 2016

Description

The "Import TMS Image" tool imports a map image from a Tile Mapping Service (TMS) using the "Geospatial Data Abstraction Library" (GDAL) by Frank Warmerdam. For more information have a look at the GDAL homepage: http://www.gdal.org GDAL Version:2.2.3
